reviewText: Geology from a Biblical creationist view.  Interesting and informative.
Fast delivery. Exactly as described. Very happy!
This contains information that most professors and teachers will ignore, or attempt to explain away. Worth the investment for me and my grandkids.

This video gives another view of how the fossil record came into being: one that involves the great flood. It is very well presented. Though I haven't decided between old earth and young earth creationism, this account does make a lot of sense, which I appreciate. I'm glad to have it in my video library. I bought this copy as a gift for someone else.
